lyrics:
lalelani Izingelosi Zihubel' ozelweyo Zithi kadunyiswe yena UmSindis' oyiNkosi Ninabantu sukumani Nihube nezingelosi Nithi, uzelwe uKristu Emzin' eBethlehema;




Refrain

Lalelan' izingelosi Zimhubel' ozelweyo.

Uyabongwa eZulwini OyiNkosi phakade Noma injalo yavuma Ukuzalwa yiNtombi Yena ongunkulunkulu Wazalwa njengomuntu Wembula uNkulunkulu Yen' onguEmmanuel;

Refrain: Lalelan' izingelosi
Zimhubel' ozelweyo.



Siyambong' othulisayo Sibong' okhanyisayo Zonk' izizwe ezimvuma Zikholwa zosindiswa Kade wayenobukhosi Sesimbon' eyingane
Ngokwehlela kwakhe lapha Sokhula thina bantu;


Refrain: Lalelan' izingelosi
Zimhubel' ozelweyo.	Amen

Bayethe, Wen’ ofayo ngenxa yethu! Sesikuzwile uthi, “Kuphelile”, Sibon’ ilanga lifiphala ngawe;

Nathi silika kanye noMaria.


Chorus:

Kodw’ uthando lwakhe lumi, Zolo, namhla, njalo, he.

Yek’ ubuhle bokumazi Umsindisi wethu lo;
Yen’ othando lwakhe lumi, Zolo, namhla, njalo, bo.
